      "raw_text": "The cut in wages announced to\ntake place some weeks ago by the\nNorthern Pacific Railway company\nhas gore into effect. The wages of\nthe section men and of coal shovelers\nhave ben reduced from $3.50 to\n$40 for 10 hours' work. Black\ndown to eight hours a day with the\nsame pay, 31h cents per hour.\n\n\nThe Gu will effect hundreds of\nmen in the city OF Spokane and many\nmore hundreds in the state.\n\n\nUnion men claim the cut in wages\nis due to nonorganization of the en-\nployes. Men doing work for the city"
    }
